libs.content:
find_library(sasl_static_library
    names sasl2 sasl libsasl
    paths ${with_sasl}/lib
    no_default_path
    no_cmake_environment_path
    no_system_environment_path)

find_library(sasl_custom_library
    names sasl2 sasl libsasl
    paths ${with_sasl}/lib
    no_default_path
    no_cmake_environment_path
    no_system_environment_path
    )

find_library(kerberos_custom_library
    names "krb5"
    paths 0/lib
    no_default_path
    no_cmake_environment_path
    no_system_environment_path
    )

find_library(openssl_library
      names ssl${pic_ext} libssl${pic_ext} ssleay32${pic_ext} ssleay32md${pic_ext}
            ssl libssl ssleay32 ssleay32md
                 hints ${openssl_win64}/lib)

find_library(crypto_library
      names crypto${pic_ext} libcrypto${pic_ext} libeay32${pic_ext}
            crypto libcrypto libeay32
                 hints ${openssl_win64}/lib)

find_program(openssl_executable openssl
        doc "path to the openssl executable")

find_library(curl_library
      names curl libcurl
      paths ${with_curl} ${with_curl}/lib
      no_default_path
      no_cmake_environment_path
      no_system_environment_path
      )

find_library(curl_library
        names libcurl_imp.lib
        paths ${with_curl} ${with_curl}/lib
        no_default_path
        no_cmake_environment_path
        no_system_environment_path
        )

find_library(ldap_custom_library
    names ldap_r ldap
    paths ${with_ldap}/lib
    no_default_path
    no_cmake_environment_path
    no_system_environment_path
    )

find_library(lber_custom_library
    names lber
    paths ${with_ldap}/lib
    no_default_path
    no_cmake_environment_path
    no_system_environment_path
    )
find_program(cat_executable cat doc "path to the executable")
find_program(awk_executable names gawk awk doc "path to the awk executable")

libs.content:
find_library(
  icu_library
  names icuuc cygicuuc cygicuuc32
  doc "libraries to link against for the common parts of icu")

find_library(
    icu_i18n_library
    names icuin icui18n cygicuin cygicuin32
    doc "libraries to link against for icu internationalization")

find_library(
      icu_data_library
    names icudt icudata cygicudata cygicudata32
    doc "libraries to link against for icu data")

find_library (libmagickwand_libraries
  names
    magickwand
    magickwand-6.q16
  paths
    /usr/lib
    /usr/local/lib
    env library_path
    env ld_library_path)

find_library (libmagickcore_libraries
  names
    magickcore
    magickcore-6.q16
  paths
    /usr/lib
    /usr/local/lib
    env library_path
    env ld_library_path)

find_library (libdwarf_libraries
  names
    dwarf libdwarf
  paths
    /usr/lib
    /usr/local/lib
    /opt/local/lib
    /sw/lib
    ${pkgconfig_libdwarf_library_dirs}
    env library_path   
    env ld_library_path)

find_library (libelf_libraries
  names
    elf
  paths
    /usr/lib
    /usr/local/lib
    /opt/local/lib
    /sw/lib
    ${pkgconfig_libelf_library_dirs}
    env library_path
    env ld_library_path)
